{"word":"G2019 - ἐπιφωνέω - epiphōnéō - ep-ee-fo-neh'-o - Cry","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιφωνέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epiphōnéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-fo-neh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Cry</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கூக்குரலிடு, ஆர்ப்பரி"},{"paragraph":"to call out to, shout"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G5455 - φωνέω - phōnéō - fo-neh'-o/5455\">G5455</a>; to <i>call at</i> something, that is, <i>exclaim:</i> - cry (against), give a shout.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2019/2019\">G2019</a>, <a href=\"#/G4856/4856\">G4856</a>, <a href=\"#/G4857/4857\">G4857</a>, <a href=\"#/G4858/4858\">G4858</a>, <a href=\"#/G4859/4859\">G4859</a>, <a href=\"#/G5455/5455\">G5455</a>, <a href=\"#/G5456/5456\">G5456</a>"}]}